data.message: Don't knowi if you read posts or not but gotta tell you EM that my husband and I are in our late 50's and enjoy your music....listened to your tracks from az to tx  rode trip to celebrate hubbies parent 60th anniversary....listened to you before we went into the church....thougjt god was going to strike us dead.............you are the best rapper ever...your beats your message your talent...............blessed be to you and your girls............would love to see you live..well that is stupid, who wants to see you dead???? continue to make great music and entertain us
